        <rdfs:comment>An editor for boolean literals, rendering as a select box with values true and false.

Also displays the current value (such as &quot;1&quot;^^xsd:boolean), but only allows to switch to true or false.</rdfs:comment>
        <rdfs:label>Boolean select editor</rdfs:label>
    </rdf:Description>
    


    <!-- http://datashapes.org/dash#ChangeScript -->


